    "In the analyzed studies, researchers have equated single LLMs both with an individual and with a population.",
    "However, many current LLMs can not guarantee stable and robust output behavior across multiple prompts and might even produce contradictory answers (Elazar et al., 2021; Kiehne et al., 2024).",
